channel.title: Main class loader help! InsidiaX V8
channel.description: [size=12pt]Hey guys, i need help with my download client for the InsidiaX client V8. I changed it to my ip and changed the java version in the compiler and run.bat and it still opens the run.bat for a split second and says cannot find main class loader or something like that. This happens for every client i try opening. Help please asap!!![/size]
